 d fluid-structure interaction methods and employ techniques\, such as late
 ncy hiding and maximizing memory bandwidth\, to effectively utilize hetero
 geneous node architectures. Collectively\, these computational development
 s and performance optimizations provide a robust and scalable framework to
  enable system-level simulations of cancer cell transport.
